  "signal_description": "The query retrieves data from the table 'defaultview-124'. It calculates various metrics related to the purchase order process. The 'Vendor Name' column is selected along with the sum of 'Last FI Invoice Item Gross Amount Document Curr.' column as 'Inv Amount'. The count of 'CASE_ID' column is calculated as 'No. of Cases'. The average confirmation time for purchase requisitions is calculated by subtracting the first 'end_time' of 'Create PR Item' event from the last 'end_time' of 'Create PO Item' event. The average processing time for purchase orders is calculated by subtracting the first 'end_time' of 'Create PO Item' event from the last 'end_time' of 'Create Goods Receipt' event. The average time from PO creation to PO release is calculated by subtracting the first 'end_time' of 'Create PO Item' event from the last 'end_time' of 'Release PO' event. The average time from PO release to goods receipt is calculated by subtracting the first 'end_time' of 'Release PO' event from the last 'end_time' of 'Create Goods Receipt' event. The average time from goods receipt to creating FI invoice is calculated by subtracting the first 'end_time' of 'Create Goods Receipt' event from the last 'end_time' of 'Create FI Invoice' event. The average time from creating FI invoice to clearing invoice is calculated by subtracting the first 'end_time' of 'Create FI Invoice' event from the last 'end_time' of 'Clear Invoice' event. Finally, the average total cycle time is calculated by subtracting the first 'end_time' from the last 'end_time'. The results are grouped by the first column (Vendor Name) and ordered by the third column (Inv Amount) in descending order."
}
